{"nodes": [{"id": "draft6_0_src_phase8_exp2_experiment_2", "label": "P8.2 \u2014 the trigger bake-off", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase8/exp2/experiment-2.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "draft6_0_src_phase8_exp2_experiment_2_tap_drift_direction", "label": "tap-drift-direction \u2014 the validated, unshipped trigger", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase8/exp2/experiment-2.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "A label-free trigger reading drift along the class/readout directions in the taps; detects real drift 8 steps earlier than the labeled error (MTD 6 vs 14) at excess-FAR 0.000, confirmed against DriftLens. Validated as spine-clean but NOT deployed \u2014 the shipped loop gates on DDM reading the namer's error-EMA instead, because the two decisions do not compose in one code path; carried as the north-star gate upgrade."}, {"id": "draft6_0_src_phase8_exp2_experiment_2_tap_drift_magnitude_null", "label": "tap-drift-magnitude \u2014 the false-fire spine null", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase8/exp2/experiment-2.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "A raw mean-shift/MMD magnitude-of-shift signal that fires on 93.8% of nuisance steps (excess-FAR 0.906) despite detecting real drift as fast as the direction signal \u2014 demonstrates 'density \u2260 class': a large covariate shift with zero class-direction change still trips a magnitude detector. Retained only as the documented false-fire null."}, {"id": "draft6_0_src_phase8_exp2_experiment_2_driftlens", "label": "DriftLens \u2014 the label-free literature reference", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase8/exp2/experiment-2.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "A purpose-built embedding-distance drift detector (Greco et al. TKDE 2025) that lands exactly on tap-drift-direction's MTD/FAR (6 steps, excess-FAR 0.000), confirming the home-grown class-direction signal is not an estimator artifact."}, {"id": "draft6_0_src_phase8_exp2_experiment_2_studd", "label": "STUDD \u2014 the conservative student-mimic trigger (degenerate here)", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase8/exp2/experiment-2.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "A student-teacher mimic-loss monitor; degenerates on this fast synthetic drift (MTD 0, always-fires, FAR 0.896) \u2014 too conservative for the stream's drift rate."}, {"id": "draft6_0_src_phase8_exp2_experiment_2_error_ema", "label": "error-EMA \u2014 labeled reference trigger, and the deployed gate input", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase8/exp2/experiment-2.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "The labeled error-rate signal; detects real drift at MTD 14 (slower than tap-drift-direction's 6, because error lags representation drift) but is the trigger the shipped DDM gate actually consumes \u2014 a legitimate labeled reference, never called spine-clean."}], "edges": [{"source": "draft6_0_src_phase8_exp2_experiment_2", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase8_exp1_experiment_1", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase8/exp2/experiment-2.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "draft6_0_src_phase8_exp2_experiment_2", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase8_exp0_experiment_0", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "draft6.0/src/phase8/exp2/experiment-2.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}